Create ReadMe.md

New Folder for Profile Picture Frame files.

Create Profile_Picture_Frame

Separate files to make up the Profile Picture Frame.

Add files via upload

- moz.png and once_a.png are the two files which are to be added in the frame.
- You'll need to select them both and set them, as shown in Screen.JPG
- Moz_Frame_Example gives an example to how the Profile Frame would look.
- The result would look like Mozillian_ProfileFrame.png for a Square image, Mozillian_ProfileFrame_Vertical.png for a 16:9 Vertical image and Mozillian_ProfileFrame_Horizontal.png for a 16:9 Horizontal image.

I hope you enjoy this frame, thanks.
